        <list id="id5866002" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-roman" mark-prefix="(" mark-suffix=")">
          <item>Which <emphasis effect="bold">materials</emphasis> will I use?</item>
        </list>
        <para id="id8127288">Evaluate and compare the different materials that you will use with regard to:</para>
        <list id="id8402787" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>availability;</item>
          <item>costs;</item>
          <item>manageable or not?</item>
          <item>durability;</item>
          <item>colours.</item>
        </list>
        <para id="id7825088">(iii) Which <emphasis effect="bold">tools</emphasis> will I use?</para>
        <para id="id4376169"> B Work safely!</para>
        <para id="id2532518">
          <figure id="id2187990">
            <media id="id2187990_media" alt="">
              <image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/graphics10-0933.png" id="id2187990__onlineimage" height="111" width="213"/>
            </media>
