        </para>
        <para id="id1170360573685">    Safety knife</para>
        <figure id="id1170360560683">
          <media id="id1170360560683_media" alt="">
            <image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/graphics11-d5cc.png" id="id1170360560683__onlineimage" height="128" width="232"/>
          </media>
        </figure>
        <para id="id8415692">Be very careful when you cut paper or cardboard. Use a safety ruler with the safety knife.</para>
        <para id="id6850565">1.4 Evaluate your products and work</para>
        <para id="id4301010">Be honest about your mistakes. Learn through it.</para>
        <para id="id1391703">A First discuss the questionnaire with your partner:</para>
        <para id="id4158407"><emphasis effect="bold"/>Did I do good <emphasis effect="bold">research</emphasis> and <emphasis effect="bold">planning</emphasis>?</para>
        <para id="id4208395">……………………………………………………………………..</para>
