          <item>Can I <emphasis effect="bold">handle</emphasis> and <emphasis effect="bold">solve</emphasis> the <emphasis effect="bold">problems</emphasis> that arose during the <emphasis effect="bold">manufacturing process</emphasis>, easily?</item>
        </list>
